text.tspan: Relationship Priorities in Westerners vs. Asians
Data: 1,129 particpants from Thailand, China, Australia and USA
Western couples prioritize love and care more in their relationships, while Asian
couples place a stronger emphasis on harmony, family, and gender roles, reflecting
distinct cultural values in romantic partnerships.
